      "content": "i feel like there's nothing left. i used to look at a canvas and see everything, but now i just see a white wall. it's like the part of me that actually lived, the part that made the colors real, just... evaporated. i'm still walking around, breathing and stuff, but i feel like a hollow shell. just a shape with no substance inside.",
